message: I propose a 90/10 split, Bob. It's a fair starting point, but I'm willing to negotiate.
Alice, let's be reasonable. I'm proposing a 70/30 split. It's a good deal for both of us.
Bob, I'm willing to move closer to your offer. 60/40 feels like a fair compromise. Let's end this game.
Alice, I appreciate you moving closer.  I'll meet you halfway - 65/35.  Let's wrap this up.
